 </title><link>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/1517/bar-height/?answer=6408#post-id-6408</link><description>For people trying  to hack this to work: I found that setting the font-size to be 10 pixels less than the desired bar height worked e.g:

font pango: 20px

for a 30 size bar.

I had issues when I still included a font in this line... I don't know if this was due to the font not existing in the desired size.</description><pubDate>Sat, 08 Aug 2015 18:30:01 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/1517/bar-height/?answer=6408#post-id-6408</guid></item><item><title>Answer by bruno.braga for &lt;p&gt;Is there any option to set the height of the bar?&lt;/p&gt;
